juniAdmin.name: juniAdmin

revisions.description: Updated for the second generation E-series products.
Added support for the second generation E-series products.
Replaced Unisphere names with Juniper names. Added 512M flash card.
Initial version of this SNMP management information module.

juniPcmciaFlashCard.name: juniPcmciaFlashCard
juniPcmciaFlashCard.description: The vendor type ID for a standard PCMCIA flash card.

juni85MegT2FlashCard.name: juni85MegT2FlashCard
juni85MegT2FlashCard.description: The vendor type ID for an 85 Megabyte Type II ATA PCMCIA flash card (Product Code: PCM-85).

juni220MegT2FlashCard.name: juni220MegT2FlashCard
juni220MegT2FlashCard.description: The vendor type ID for a 220 Megabyte Type II ATA PCMCIA flash card (Product Code: FLASH-220M).

juni512MegT2FlashCard.name: juni512MegT2FlashCard
juni512MegT2FlashCard.description: The vendor type ID for a 512 Megabyte Type II ATA PCMCIA flash card (Product Code: RX-FLASH512-FRU).

juni1GigT2FlashCard.name: juni1GigT2FlashCard
juni1GigT2FlashCard.description: The vendor type ID for a 1 Gigabyte Type II ATA PCMCIA flash card (Product Code: ERX-FLASH1GB-FRU).

juniTraceRouteImplementationTypes.name: juniTraceRouteImplementationTypes
juniTraceRouteImplementationTypes.description: The registration node (point) for Juniper Traceroute implementation types.

juniTraceRouteUsingIcmpProbe.name: juniTraceRouteUsingIcmpProbe
